Version:             0.1
Synopsis:            Netlink communication for Haskell
Homepage:            http://netlink-hs.googlecode.com/
License:             BSD3
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              David Anderson
Maintainer:          dave@natulte.net
Copyright:           Google Inc. 2010
Stability:           Alpha
Category:            System
Build-type:          Simple
